</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The stylized history of financial exch=
anges is something like:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-=
left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Once, a d=
ozen or so big brokers met under <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/35159763.283346/aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvQnV0=
