yLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">a tree</=
a> or whatever to trade their stuff.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px=
;">They collectively set some rules for trading the stuff, which evolved in=
to a nonprofit membership organization =E2=80=94=C2=A0an =E2=80=9Cexchange=
=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94 run by the big brokers.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 5px;">The exchange charged fees to trade, it invested in technology, an=
d it eventually made sense for the exchange to restructure and go public as=
 a=C2=A0for-profit company.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The do=
zen or so big brokers, who once owned and ran the exchange, don=E2=80=99t a=
nymore: It=E2=80=99s a public company, they=E2=80=99ve sold whatever shares=
 they had in it, it=E2=80=99s just an arm=E2=80=99s-length counterparty now=
.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">They don=E2=80=99t like paying t=
he fees.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">They get to talking with =
each other.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">=E2=80=9CAt the end of=
 the day,=E2=80=9D they say, =E2=80=9Cthis exchange is really just=C2=A0<em=
>us</em>. It=E2=80=99s a venue =E2=80=94=C2=A0now a computer system, not a =
tree, but still =E2=80=94=C2=A0where the 12 of us get together to trade stu=
ff with each other. Why are we paying these fees to a for-profit exchange? =
Why don=E2=80=99t we just meet together somewhere=C2=A0<em>else</em>, trade=
 with each other, and save on fees?=E2=80=9D</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bot=
tom: 5px;">They can=E2=80=99t literally meet under a different tree, since =
now everything is computerized, but if they talk about this enough eventual=
ly an entrepreneur will go and build it for them.</li></ol><p style=3D"marg=
in: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35=
159763.283346/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwM=
